extendedInfo.description: Stupid Fly Records has launched a brand new mobile app that isn't just a way to keep you up-to-date with our release schedule but it also puts our radio station (Stupid Fly Radio w/ dj mixes by the artists) in the palm of your hands.         This app has plenty of networking features like, Facebook, YouTube and Twitter so you can catch up with us and find out what we are up to, say hello or send us a demo. We also have an interactive Facebook feature so you can log-in and send us photos!        Thanks to Soundcloud and Conduit Mobile, the App is absolutely FREE and no advertisements!! So grab it now!

reviews.comment: If ya dont know, now ya know. Stupid fly takin ovah!
reviews.author: A Google User
